<span id="freeTextContainer18066998204122241833">Timothy &quot;Tim&quot; William Burton is a prolific American film director/writer, best known for the dark imagery and quirky nature of his popular films. He is also the author and illustrator of the poetry collection &quot;The Melancholy Death of Oyster Boy &amp; Other Stories.&quot;</span>
  <span id="freeText18066998204122241833" style="display:none">Timothy "Tim" William Burton is a prolific American film director/writer, best known for the dark imagery and quirky nature of his popular films. He is also the author and illustrator of the poetry collection "The Melancholy Death of Oyster Boy &amp; Other Stories."</span>
  <a data-text-id="18066998204122241833" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

